data.name: FintechDB
data.query:
select customer_name, customer_id as customerNumber, category_name as asset_category, name as asset_name, sum(customer_score) as customerScore,
MIN(price) as price, 
MIN ((tmp.quantity_order)*100/(tmp.quantity_in_stock+tmp.quantity_order)) as xrr, 
sum(tmp.total_order) as trade_volume, 
sum(tmp.quantity_order) as trade_quantity from 
(SELECT o.id, c.name as customer_name,
o.created_at, o.customer_id, c.customer_score,
od.product_id, od.quantity_order, od.price_each, c.credit_limit, pl.category_name, 
p.name, p.quantity_in_stock, p.price, (od.quantity_order*od.price_each) as total_order
FROM fintech.trades o
JOIN fintech.trade_details od ON o.id = od.order_id
JOIN fintech.assets p ON od.product_id = p.id
JOIN fintech.traders c ON o.customer_id = c.id
JOIN fintech.asset_categories pl ON p.category_id = pl.id) tmp
group by asset_name, asset_category, customerNumber, customer_name;
